author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Protector Forsikring ASA Reports Profit Before Tax Totaled To NOK 1362 Million For Quarter​
text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Protector Forsikring Asa:
* ‍PROFIT BEFORE TAX TOTALED TO NOK 136,2 MILLION FOR QUARTER​
* SAYS GROSS WRITTEN PREMIUM INCREASED WITH 21,1% IN 2017 AND 37,7% IN QUARTER
* ‍SEES NET COMBINED RATIO FOR 2018 BETWEEN 92 PERCENT TO 94 PERCENT​ Further company coverage:
